                "text": "Simply paste your Base64 string into the text area above. The decoder automatically strips the data:image prefix if present, validates the string, and displays the decoded image. You can then download it using the download button."
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "Is my data safe when using this decoder?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "Yes, absolutely. This tool runs entirely in your browser using JavaScript. No data is uploaded to any server. Your Base64 strings and decoded images never leave your device, ensuring complete privacy."
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
